{
  "stem": "23090.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had an  aunt that lived in-- with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, in our-- in the way we lived in our particular-- our place was an apartment building.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all our relatives basically were on the various floors, so it was very easy to-- I shouldn't say all, but there was a goodly number of us that lived in the same apartment.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was quite a large complex.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were able to gather quite often and-- and exchange both the good things and the bad things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when the-- when the wars were approaching and the bombings we heard on a daily basis, we would gather at each others' homes and discuss it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I say 'we,' the elders did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as a child, this was a very scary and a very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] dismal existence, because all you were-- you were forming some very bad things in the mind, and virtually walked around scared on a continuous basis.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, in a way, it was wonderful to do this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, in-- in retrospect now, as I look back, it is not good sometimes to have children under conditions that-- that when you discuss potential annihilation or potential destruction, or being annihilated on a mass basis, you sort of don't know how to cope with that.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you are basically scared throughout that whole time and existence.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So The gathering of a family unit was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the tales, as we say, around the fireplace were-- just scared the hell out of me and my cousins.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and until the end of the war, we were just-- we were just constantly living under that fear.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We'll come back to the war in a bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Can you tell me, though, about gatherings, family gatherings, perhaps, before the war?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
